== Description ==
{{:KZDoom}}Built within the same year as [[KZDoom1]], the second episode of the [[KZDoom]] series takes the same basic principle and expands upon it, improving it in the process. It also adds some modified tree sprites and ambience from Quake 2 in order to increase the realism. Expect to fight your way through tight battles with your sped-up shotgun against the more aggressive basic enemies before stepping outside, into the mercy of the cacodemons.
